formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: This is a government project the books of accounts are maintained on cash basis hence whatever expenses are claimed as incurred and paid is either claimed basis the earlier certificate or the debit transactions in the bank statement made available to us and to ascertain the cost management representation is relied upon. The previous consultant had shown all the construction cost in onsite expenditure while registering the project hence we have shown the construction expenditure as part of onsite expenditure promoter is advised to make the required details rectified with the RERA Authorities.  Promoter is maintaining a single RERA Account and hence all the amounts of booking are deposited in the same account. Booking Details KYC ID Mobile number of the allottee etc is taken as provided by the management . Details pertaining to the carpet area/ balcony area etc is taken as provided by the management. While registering the project the previous consultant has shown the blocks as A, B and C however actually the blocks are numbered as F and I. The units mentioned as C block is actually shops  which would be unbooked. We do not take the responsibility of the KYC Id of the allottees in the absence of the sufficient documents. RERA Bank details are taken as provided by the management.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation. As informed to us by the management there is no loan or encumbrance either on the project or on the units offered to sale. We have errorneously uploaded incomplete Form 3A however we shall correct the error in the next return as the same cannot be corrected now. Bank balance and withdrawl from RERA A/c is taken as per withdrawl amounts mentioned in Bank Statement. there was error in closing balance of bank submitted in last quarter the same has been corrected now and adjustment is made in deposit account. To arrive at withdrawl amount we have reduced closing bank balance from the total booking deposit received. Also they have collected 57000/- towards electricity and gas connection and 75000/- towards maint. however due to insufficient details provided the same has not been updated in the details of the receipt.
